              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FISCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Double Frisch-Gridded ionization chamber as",
                "        fission fragment detector. Used in flow mode",
                "        with P-10 gas mixture."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " As neutron detector, DEMON modules were used",
                " 16 cm in diameter and 20 cm in length, having 4 litres",
                " volumes filled with BC501A liquid scintillator and",
                " coupled to 130mm diameter XP512B photomultiplier.",
                " Neutron registration efficiency was found to be 0.13.",
                " Taking into account geometrical efficiency of experi-",
                " mental arrangement, the overall neutron detection",
                " efficiency amounts to 0.06."
              ]
            }
          ],
